items.name: Spotify-Premium
items.description: This repository provides a method to simulate premium features on Spotify for educational purposes. It includes scripts and tools that demonstrate how certain premium functionalities can be replicated in a non-premium account.

items.name: SolaraEx3cutor
items.description: Solara is a powerful and intuitive Roblox script executor designed to enhance your gaming experience. Whether you're exploring new game mechanics, testing your own creations, or simply curious about what's possible in Roblox, Solara provides the tools you need.

items.name: Ableton-Live-Suite
items.description: This repository provides resources and tools for exploring Ableton Live Suite features without requiring a paid license. It includes scripts and configurations that mimic the functionality of Ableton Live Suite for educational and testing purposes.
